(METAL GENTLY CLANKING)

00:12.067 --> 00:14.000
(VEHICLE APPROACHING)

00:22.833 --> 00:25.000
(PASSENGER DOOR CLOSES)

00:27.733 --> 00:29.733
(WIND WHISTLING)

00:33.167 --> 00:35.333
(BIRD SHRIEKS)

00:37.000 --> 00:43.074
Advertise your product or brand here
